seeing him this way.

11:26.696 --> 11:29.432
So, when was the last time
you talked to him?

11:29.465 --> 11:31.133
They called
for my birthday.

11:31.167 --> 11:33.135
So...

11:33.169 --> 11:35.838
May, I guess.

11:35.872 --> 11:39.108
Last time I saw him,
he was barely there.

11:39.141 --> 11:40.810
How long
you gonna be here?

11:40.843 --> 11:44.046
About a week, I guess.

11:44.080 --> 11:46.482
Friday, maybe.

11:46.515 --> 11:49.619
You still at the post office?

11:51.888 --> 11:55.391
Not... anymore.

11:58.661 --> 12:00.930
We can't leave her
alone out here.

12:03.532 --> 12:07.470
We should've done something.

12:07.503 --> 12:08.905
Hugged her? Something.

12:08.938 --> 12:11.841
Yeah. Yeah.

12:11.874 --> 12:15.478
'Cause that would've made
everything better, probably.

12:23.220 --> 12:24.921
I'm gonna take a shower.

14:12.195 --> 14:14.930
What is it?

14:14.964 --> 14:17.933
It's just the wind.

