Don't let her fall.

19:21.170 --> 19:22.339
I got you.

19:22.372 --> 19:24.073
I got you.

20:37.112 --> 20:38.314
No, no.

20:38.348 --> 20:40.350
You sit. You're...
You're alright.

20:51.361 --> 20:53.128
I'm so sorry.

20:55.665 --> 20:58.234
I made y'all some food.

20:58.268 --> 21:01.604
It's a roast.

21:01.638 --> 21:04.374
Thank you.

21:14.584 --> 21:18.188
I didn't want
to say anything before.

21:18.221 --> 21:20.323
It... It wasn't my place.

21:23.158 --> 21:25.195
Your mama...

21:25.228 --> 21:28.298
She was saying things.

21:28.331 --> 21:30.966
Talkin' when she thought
I wasn't listenin'.

21:33.403 --> 21:36.639
I didn't like it.

21:36.673 --> 21:39.576
What did she say?

21:39.609 --> 21:43.011
She would sit...

21:43.045 --> 21:45.482
right beside him
just whispering.

21:48.083 --> 21:50.420
But she wasn't talking to him.

21:52.489 --> 21:53.656
Not like she used to.

21:53.690 --> 21:55.558
It was like...

21:55.592 --> 21:59.529
there was someone else.

21:59.562 --> 22:02.565
Someone here.

22:02.599 --> 22:05.768
I thought it'd be better
with her family close by.

22:05.802 --> 22:09.137
I prayed for them.

22:14.477 --> 22:18.581
She was taking care
of him herself at night.

22:18.615 --> 22:22.485
I can set something up now,
if you want.

22:22.519 --> 22:26.289
It might be better for y'all,
if... if someone was here.

22:26.322 --> 22:28.191
Is there anything we can do.

22:28.224 --> 22:31.194
If we took him to the hospital,
would that change anything?

22:31.227 --> 22:33.596
I'll stay in here overnight.

22:33.630 --> 22:35.231
