22:35.265 --> 22:37.267
- If you show me.
- I just think you c...

22:37.300 --> 22:39.702
This is what they wanted.

24:07.523 --> 24:09.459
Go on that other side.

24:11.828 --> 24:13.696
Put 'em in this corner, Charlie.

24:39.822 --> 24:42.392
Wait.

25:00.243 --> 25:03.546
Started bringing
different ones up here.

25:03.579 --> 25:07.350
Had a few certain favorites.

25:07.383 --> 25:09.652
I forgot about Vida.

25:21.397 --> 25:24.634
Who was she talking to?

25:24.667 --> 25:26.502
Don't do that.

25:26.536 --> 25:27.770
It doesn't matter.

25:27.804 --> 25:30.873
She didn't know
what she was doing.

25:30.907 --> 25:32.742
Why would you say that?

25:32.775 --> 25:35.712
She chopped up her own
fuckin' fingers in the kitchen.

25:35.745 --> 25:36.913
She made herself die.

25:36.946 --> 25:38.514
Jesus Christ!

25:38.548 --> 25:40.416
Well, it ain't gonna make sense.

25:40.450 --> 25:42.218
Ever.

25:43.820 --> 25:45.354
We should've talked to her!

25:45.388 --> 25:47.290
Yeah, we didn't!

26:06.809 --> 26:08.344
Hey...

26:08.377 --> 26:10.413
That's okay.

26:55.124 --> 26:57.360
I need three fuckin' minutes.

27:03.566 --> 27:07.036
Michael!

27:14.110 --> 27:16.979
- Dad's in here!
- Louise?!

27:36.899 --> 27:39.635
He <i>wa</i> in there.

27:39.669 --> 27:42.605
Fuck.

27:42.638 --> 27:43.806
Fuck!

27:45.908 --> 27:47.443
Do you want
to talk about it?

27:47.476 --> 27:50.012
No.

27:50.046 --> 27:52.448
I'm gonna go have a cigarette.

27:52.481 --> 27:55.718
I'll come out there with you.

27:57.119 --> 27:59.522
It's stupid.

27:59.555 --> 28:01.924
I feel stupid.

28:31.787 --> 28:33.890
I don't want to talk about it.

28:53.843 --> 28:56.479
I found Mom's diary.

29:03.719 --> 29:05.788
Did you look in it?

29:05.821 --> 29:09.125
I read the last page.

29:12.161 --> 29:14.096
What does it say?

29:20.203 --> 29:21.737
"I know he's there,

29:21.771 --> 29:23.472
in the darkness.

29:23.506 --> 29:24.573
Help me.

29:24.607 --> 29:26.909
Help me, please.

29:26.943 --> 29:29.145
He's killing David.

29:29.179 --> 29:32.249
He can't breathe anymore.

29:32.282 --> 29:35.185
There's nothing
I can do to stop it.

29:37.987 --> 29:40.623
Devil, devil, devil.

29:44.927 --> 29:48.864
He wants...

29:48.898 --> 29:53.002
David's soul."

30:03.612 --> 30:07.184
How'd she get up there?

30:07.217 --> 30:09.952
That cop said the tub,

30:09.986 --> 30:11.587
but you moved it.

30:13.756 --> 30:15.958
What?

30:15.992 --> 30:18.027
She was a couple feet in the air
where we found her.

30:18.060 --> 30:20.629
How'd she get
up there like that?

30:26.336 --> 30:28.637
I don't know.

30:32.342 --> 30:35.144
"The voices in my head...

30:38.614 --> 30:42.185
<i>His</i> voice...

30:42.219 --> 30:45.921
He makes me want to die.

30:45.955 --> 30:48.325
I locked the door,

30:48.358 --> 30:50.626
but he came inside the room.

30:50.659 --> 30:53.729
I want David to wake up.

30:53.763 --> 30:55.931
I grab his hand.
I squeeze it.

30:55.965 --> 30:57.833
- Wake up!"
- Please stop.

30:57.867 --> 31:00.603
"That sound...

31:00.636 --> 31:03.340
so many mouths.

31:03.373 --> 31:05.708
He climbs on the bed.

31:05.741 --> 31:07.176
He hurts David.

31:07.210 --> 31:09.078
- I can hear him."
- Louise!

31:09.111 --> 31:11.680
"I see him.

31:13.316 --> 31:15.185
He...

31:15.218 --> 31:18.621
He laughs at me.

31:18.654 --> 31:20.756
He kills me.

31:23.626 --> 31:25.195
I'm already dead.

31:28.331 --> 31:29.865
<i>I'm dead."</i>

31:50.119 --> 31:51.654
Thank you, Tim.

31:51.687 --> 31:54.623
I know you don't do this,
but we just...

31:54.657 --> 31:55.991
Oh, no, you're fine.

31:56.025 --> 31:57.626
You're fine, Mike.

32:06.168 --> 32:08.737
Thought you might like these.

32:08.771 --> 32:11.874
We found it in her pocket.

32:11.907 --> 32:13.310
What is it?

32:13.343 --> 32:17.347
Those are crosses
they give out in Sunday School.

32:17.380 --> 32:19.682
At least they did
when I was little.

32:23.986 --> 32:25.888
Maybe she collected them.

32:31.894 --> 32:35.030
She... She doesn't.

32:35.064 --> 32:41.070
She... She didn't... go.

32:41.103 --> 32:44.006
You want to get started
on the paperwork?

32:44.039 --> 32:45.208
Yes, please.

32:45.242 --> 32:46.675
Thank you.

33:33.822 --> 33:35.492
It's okay.

33:35.525 --> 33:36.892
It's okay.

33:36.926 --> 33:38.928
It's okay.

33:38.961 --> 33:40.197
It's okay.

33:46.436 --> 33:48.971
It's okay.

33:56.946 --> 33:58.181
Jesus!

34:09.292 --> 34:12.362
Everything alright?

34:12.395 --> 34:14.797
I...

34:14.830 --> 34:16.832
I...

34:20.836 --> 34:24.241
I thought there was a spider.

34:24.274 --> 34:27.876
There was a spider.

34:27.910 --> 34:29.912
Did you get it?

34:29.945 --> 34:31.880
Um...

34:34.850 --> 34:36.785
It was nothing.

34:51.534 --> 34:54.970
I'm gonna get some sleep.

34:55.004 --> 34:57.973
I'm gonna grab some groceries
in the morning.

35:00.843 --> 35:02.412
Goodnight.

