41:09.412 --> 41:11.280
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

41:11.314 --> 41:13.516
<i>You have reached a number
that is disconnected,</i>

41:13.549 --> 41:15.451
<i>or is no longer in service.</i>

41:15.485 --> 41:18.221
<i>If you feel you have reached
this recording in error,</i>

41:18.254 --> 41:20.957
<i>please check the number
and try your call again.</i>

41:28.231 --> 41:30.433
Hello?

41:30.466 --> 41:32.669
<i>Told y'all not to come.</i>

42:10.306 --> 42:12.275
Can I help you?

42:12.308 --> 42:14.243
Michael.

42:17.480 --> 42:20.616
Now, I was hoping
we might have a little talk.

42:22.452 --> 42:24.987
You look like your mother.

42:28.558 --> 42:31.794
"I won't know if it's them,

42:31.828 --> 42:34.897
but I hear their voices.

42:34.931 --> 42:37.266
They call.

42:37.300 --> 42:40.870
But what if it's a lie.

42:40.903 --> 42:44.340
He won't stop.

42:44.373 --> 42:47.443
They will die.

42:47.477 --> 42:50.713
We're dead already.

42:50.747 --> 42:55.017
Spiders on my face like tears."

42:55.051 --> 42:57.553
Mm, my, my, my.

42:57.587 --> 42:59.288
Mm.

42:59.322 --> 43:01.357
I started coming to see her.

43:01.390 --> 43:02.892
She was...

43:02.925 --> 43:06.596
She was scared and alone.

43:09.031 --> 43:12.969
I was here for her.

43:13.002 --> 43:16.773
I-I wanted to meet you.

43:16.806 --> 43:21.711
She loves you both so much.

43:21.744 --> 43:23.045
I just thought...

43:23.079 --> 43:25.515
if you like, I can help.

43:25.548 --> 43:28.951
I think you've done enough.

43:28.985 --> 43:31.821
I didn't know about any of this.

43:34.123 --> 43:36.526
This didn't happen overnight.

43:36.559 --> 43:38.928
She had thoughts in her head.

43:38.961 --> 43:42.732
They came from somewhere.

43:42.765 --> 43:45.434
You came to the house.
You were here.

43:45.468 --> 43:48.104
You want to understand, yeah.

43:48.137 --> 43:50.873
She didn't believe in God.

43:50.907 --> 43:52.441
Never did.

43:52.475 --> 43:53.876
None of us do.

43:53.910 --> 43:56.813
My mom thought
the devil was here.

43:56.846 --> 43:58.714
She didn't believe.

43:58.748 --> 44:01.651
What does it matter
whether you believe.

44:01.684 --> 44:05.955
You think the wolf cares
if you believe he's a wolf?

44:05.988 --> 44:07.757
Hmm?

44:07.790 --> 44:11.894
Not if he finds you
alone in the woods.

44:11.928 --> 44:13.796
What did you say to her?

44:13.830 --> 44:18.067
I told her the... the truth.

44:18.100 --> 44:21.070
No, you told her <i>your</i> truth.

44:23.172 --> 44:24.874
Well, maybe so.

44:24.907 --> 44:26.642
Yeah, well, then I guess

44:26.676 --> 44:30.680
the same could be said
about you and yours.

44:33.149 --> 44:34.684
I think you need to go.

44:34.717 --> 44:36.853
- Michael.
- This isn't helping us.

44:36.886 --> 44:39.689
I didn't want to upset you.

44:39.722 --> 44:41.791
Well, you do,
and I'm not gonna sit here

44:41.824 --> 44:43.960
and pretend like
you didn't feed her this shit.

44:46.062 --> 44:49.031
She needed someone.

44:49.065 --> 44:53.536
I think you both
know that now, hmm?

44:53.569 --> 44:55.905
She was alone.

44:55.938 --> 44:59.041
They both were.

44:59.075 --> 45:01.110
I didn't do that.

45:01.143 --> 45:03.813
I helped.

45:03.846 --> 45:05.147
Did you?

45:05.182 --> 45:08.084
Yes. I did.

45:13.190 --> 45:15.625
- How's your father?
- He's fine.

45:15.658 --> 45:17.860
Well, that's good.

45:17.894 --> 45:19.795
I think about him a lot.

45:24.066 --> 45:27.003
You really think
the devil's out there?

45:27.036 --> 45:28.971
That's your truth?

45:34.176 --> 45:37.880
Your mama died, hmm.

45:37.914 --> 45:40.816
You heard her words,

45:40.850 --> 45:43.220
her warning.

45:43.253 --> 45:46.722
You think she's crazy
because she saw a wolf,

45:46.756 --> 45:50.159
saw him coming?

45:50.193 --> 45:53.963
He's not out there.

45:53.996 --> 45:56.632
He's already here.

46:35.171 --> 46:37.039
I don't know
what she wants to do.

46:37.073 --> 46:38.774
I can't tell.

46:38.808 --> 46:42.611
The whole thing's so fucked.

46:42.645 --> 46:44.847
I just want to come home.

46:44.880 --> 46:48.551
Mom was all I had left.

46:52.555 --> 46:54.924
I just miss her.

47:11.841 --> 47:14.043
Oh, no, you stay there.

47:14.076 --> 47:15.845
I told you.

47:20.850 --> 47:22.885
Baby, I walk around here, and...

47:22.918 --> 47:26.622
I don't feel anything.

47:46.343 --> 47:50.280
How are my babies?

47:50.313 --> 47:52.615
Give them a hug for me.

47:56.186 --> 47:58.788
I love you.

47:58.821 --> 48:01.724
"He...

48:01.757 --> 48:04.827
He is...

48:04.860 --> 48:06.629
watching.

48:08.265 --> 48:11.133
He waits.

48:11.167 --> 48:15.638
He is...

48:15.671 --> 48:18.741
everywhere."

48:28.918 --> 48:32.154
Michael?

48:36.659 --> 48:37.827
Hello?

48:40.963 --> 48:43.866
Is someone out there?

48:59.715 --> 49:01.817
She wasn't crazy.

49:04.354 --> 49:06.289
<i>I'm</i> not crazy.

49:08.858 --> 49:11.694
What if she saw something...

49:11.727 --> 49:13.129
out there?

49:17.334 --> 49:19.902
I saw something.

49:22.339 --> 49:24.974
And it wasn't a fuckin' dream.

49:26.842 --> 49:28.177
I wasn't imagining things,

49:28.211 --> 49:31.448
'cause that doesn't happen.

49:31.481 --> 49:33.416
Look at me.

49:40.290 --> 49:42.892
Mom was standing...

49:42.925 --> 49:44.693
right there.

49:49.266 --> 49:51.834
I saw it through the window

49:51.867 --> 49:53.436
last night.

49:57.840 --> 49:59.775
But it wasn't her.

50:03.413 --> 50:05.781
It was fucking scary, Louise.

50:08.518 --> 50:10.986
It can't be real.

50:59.868 --> 51:01.804
There's something out there.

51:45.981 --> 51:49.552
You should come outside.

51:49.586 --> 51:52.855
It's that priest.

51:52.888 --> 51:54.990
The hell?

52:12.542 --> 52:15.978
Come outside.

52:16.011 --> 52:18.047
What are you doing here?

52:18.080 --> 52:20.450
It's like 3:00 in the morning.

52:20.483 --> 52:23.919
Come outside.

52:23.952 --> 52:26.088
You can't just show up here!

52:29.292 --> 52:30.427
Wait.

52:30.460 --> 52:32.161
Don't wait.

52:37.667 --> 52:39.536
You want some rope?

52:40.603 --> 52:43.340
Oh, Jesus.

52:51.080 --> 52:52.248
Michael...

52:52.282 --> 52:54.049
Where'd he fucking go?

53:02.592 --> 53:03.959
He's not out here.

53:19.342 --> 53:21.009
Don't answer it.

53:25.715 --> 53:27.484
Don't!

53:44.334 --> 53:46.436
Come on.

53:48.571 --> 53:51.641
Come on, Michael.
Pick up the phone.

54:06.689 --> 54:08.391
Who's there?!

54:17.300 --> 54:18.967
Alright.

54:55.305 --> 54:57.674
You get out of here.
You don't belong here.

54:57.707 --> 54:59.275
You get, now, come on!

54:59.309 --> 55:02.044
Alright, demon, get.

55:15.391 --> 55:17.260
What do you want?

55:17.293 --> 55:18.461
What do you want?!

55:18.495 --> 55:19.729
Just... Just say it!

55:31.708 --> 55:36.679
<i>You did this to me.</i>

55:52.662 --> 55:54.230
There's no tracks,

55:54.264 --> 55:56.131
no footprints.

55:56.164 --> 55:58.100
Did Charlie ever meet the guy?

55:58.133 --> 55:59.469
Charlie hasn't answered
his phone in two days.

55:59.502 --> 56:00.670
I keep calling.

56:03.239 --> 56:05.542
He was just...
just standing out there,

56:05.575 --> 56:08.143
just waiting for me.

56:08.176 --> 56:10.280
We take dad to a hospital.

56:13.850 --> 56:16.386
We can't keep him here,
not anymore.

56:22.725 --> 56:25.194
We'll get the doctor out here.

56:27.497 --> 56:30.132
You saw his face, didn't you?

56:33.303 --> 56:34.270
You saw it when the...

56:34.304 --> 56:36.071
It can't be real.

56:57.493 --> 56:59.195
Father Thorne?

56:59.228 --> 57:00.563
<i>Who is this?</i>

57:00.597 --> 57:02.465
This is Louise Straker.

57:02.498 --> 57:04.867
We met yesterday.

57:04.901 --> 57:06.903
You came to see us.

57:06.936 --> 57:09.505
<i>Well,
how did you get this number?</i>

57:09.539 --> 57:12.275
You gave it to me.

57:12.308 --> 57:16.245
<i>This is a hotel.
Y-You called my room.</i>

57:16.279 --> 57:18.648
<i>Where are you calling from?</i>

57:18.681 --> 57:20.550
I'm in Thurber.

57:20.583 --> 57:22.285
You were here yesterday.

57:22.318 --> 57:24.520
We met yesterday.
You know my mother.

57:24.554 --> 57:26.222
<i>Thurber? Where is...</i>

57:26.255 --> 57:27.657
You were here.

57:29.325 --> 57:31.527
Thurber.

57:31.561 --> 57:33.596
Thurber, Texas.

57:33.630 --> 57:36.199
<i>I've never been to Texas.</i>

57:36.232 --> 57:38.166
<i>I'm in Chicago.</i>

57:41.971 --> 57:43.673
You don't know Virginia Straker?

57:43.706 --> 57:44.907
<i>Are you trying to be funny?</i>

57:44.941 --> 57:46.776
- But...
- <i>Her name was Louise.</i>

57:46.809 --> 57:48.578
Wait.

57:48.611 --> 57:52.548
<i>I guess
you know that, don't you?</i>

57:52.582 --> 57:56.219
<i>You know I had a daughter.</i>

57:56.252 --> 57:58.454
I don't know how.

57:58.488 --> 58:01.791
Sir, I didn't...
I didn't mean to...

58:01.824 --> 58:03.760
<i>She killed herself...</i>

58:03.793 --> 58:05.895
<i>a long time ago.</i>

58:08.331 --> 58:11.367
<i>Why would you do this?</i>

58:11.401 --> 58:15.371
Sir, I'm sorry.
I didn't mean...

58:15.405 --> 58:17.340
<i>You sound just like her.</i>

58:41.330 --> 58:44.367
Have you, um...

58:44.400 --> 58:48.337
noticed any changes
since you've arrived?

58:48.371 --> 58:50.573
We just want to take him
to a hospital,

58:50.606 --> 58:53.509
so do we need
to fill out some forms

58:53.543 --> 58:56.279
or whatever you need.

58:56.312 --> 58:58.614
I doubt he'd make it
to the highway.

59:01.818 --> 59:04.554
He's getting weaker every day,

59:04.587 --> 59:06.289
and I don't think I can just...

59:06.322 --> 59:08.691
A whole lot has changed.

59:08.725 --> 59:12.829
But I can't sign off
on moving him.

59:12.862 --> 59:16.432
It's just too late for that.

59:16.466 --> 59:18.434
He shouldn't be here.

59:20.603 --> 59:22.004
Is there a problem
with his treatment?

59:22.038 --> 59:23.406
You're not listening.

59:23.439 --> 59:25.341
- I'm trying.
- It's our choice.

59:25.374 --> 59:27.343
And I can't let you kill him.

59:32.682 --> 59:35.818
We just want him safe.

59:58.875 --> 1:00:01.611
You must see people
at their weakest.

1:00:01.644 --> 1:00:03.746
It's got to take a toll on you.

1:00:05.715 --> 1:00:09.318
It's not all I see.

1:00:09.352 --> 1:00:11.621
There's a lot of love.

1:00:13.890 --> 1:00:16.859
It's a silly thing to say,
but it's true.

1:00:18.661 --> 1:00:22.598
Sometimes I'm the only one...

1:00:22.632 --> 1:00:24.901
when it happens, you know.

1:00:27.370 --> 1:00:30.006
I'm just...

1:00:30.039 --> 1:00:31.841
the worst thing in the world

1:00:31.874 --> 1:00:35.044
to me is...
for a person to die alone.

1:00:43.786 --> 1:00:45.888
My mom...

1:00:45.922 --> 1:00:50.726
She thought something
was coming for him.

1:00:50.760 --> 1:00:53.496
My dad was good.

1:00:53.529 --> 1:00:57.133
Michael...

1:00:57.166 --> 1:00:59.635
I can see the fear in y'all.

1:01:03.039 --> 1:01:05.007
I can feel it in this house.

1:01:07.977 --> 1:01:10.112
I know y'all don't
believe in God,

1:01:10.146 --> 1:01:13.916
and that's fine...

1:01:13.950 --> 1:01:16.853
but I do,

1:01:16.886 --> 1:01:19.622
and I think there are
things in this world...

1:01:19.655 --> 1:01:23.559
horrible things...

1:01:23.593 --> 1:01:24.994
wicked...

1:01:27.730 --> 1:01:30.900
...and they come
for whoever they want.

1:01:30.933 --> 1:01:34.770
But there's love here.

1:01:36.806 --> 1:01:39.442
And a soul needs love
to keep it safe.

1:01:42.178 --> 1:01:44.847
I hope you're right.

1:01:44.881 --> 1:01:46.983
So do I.

1:03:03.226 --> 1:03:04.593
Wolves wouldn't do this...

1:03:04.627 --> 1:03:06.829
not this way, not like this.

1:03:06.862 --> 1:03:07.964
No.

1:03:12.202 --> 1:03:15.104
I'll call another hospital.

1:03:15.137 --> 1:03:17.240
Get another doctor
here tomorrow.

1:03:21.677 --> 1:03:24.647
She told us not to come.

1:03:24.680 --> 1:03:28.684
God damn it!

1:03:53.142 --> 1:03:56.579
How many are still out there?

1:03:56.612 --> 1:03:58.948
I don't know.

1:03:58.981 --> 1:04:01.083
Five, maybe.

1:04:04.887 --> 1:04:07.623
We check again in the morning,

1:04:07.656 --> 1:04:11.027
but I think we got
what was left.

1:04:11.060 --> 1:04:12.928
There was a mama due.

1:04:12.962 --> 1:04:15.232
I saw her.

1:04:15.265 --> 1:04:19.568
I'm gonna go out there
and sit with them,

1:04:19.602 --> 1:04:21.704
- make sure...
- Don't.

1:04:24.173 --> 1:04:26.642
Well, I'm not just
gonna let them die.

1:04:28.744 --> 1:04:31.281
Not today.

1:04:31.314 --> 1:04:34.284
If I'm here, I'm gonna work.

1:04:36.186 --> 1:04:38.288
Then let me go with you.

1:04:40.923 --> 1:04:43.125
You stay with him.

1:04:44.894 --> 1:04:47.297
Please.

1:04:47.330 --> 1:04:51.033
I was in there with Dad
earlier today,

1:04:51.067 --> 1:04:54.204
and that nurse said something
that's been sticking with me.

1:04:56.005 --> 1:05:00.176
There's nothing worse than
a soul left alone in the end.

1:05:04.914 --> 1:05:08.684
She wanted me to feel something,

1:05:08.717 --> 1:05:12.721
and I wanted to feel something.

1:05:20.796 --> 1:05:23.766
Now I just want to forget
about this place.

1:05:27.937 --> 1:05:29.872
I'm scared.

1:05:32.074 --> 1:05:33.776
Me too.

1:05:47.723 --> 1:05:49.925
There you go.

1:05:49.959 --> 1:05:51.294
That's a good mama.

1:05:51.328 --> 1:05:52.928
Good mama.

1:05:55.332 --> 1:05:57.733
Good girl.
You a good girl?

1:05:57.766 --> 1:06:00.936
You good girl, mm?

1:06:16.986 --> 1:06:19.189
Go on.

1:06:42.178 --> 1:06:43.979
Jesus, Becky.

1:06:55.392 --> 1:06:56.393
Hello?

1:06:59.895 --> 1:07:01.464
Hello?

1:07:06.101 --> 1:07:07.736
Who's out there?

1:07:15.844 --> 1:07:17.480
Go on, get!

1:07:19.549 --> 1:07:21.850
Go!

1:07:25.288 --> 1:07:32.127
♪ Every trials
and temptations ♪

1:07:32.161 --> 1:07:34.364
Go away.

1:07:34.397 --> 1:07:39.902
♪ Is there trouble anywhere? ♪

1:07:39.935 --> 1:07:46.108
♪ What a friend we have
in Jesus ♪

1:07:55.552 --> 1:07:57.886
You're not real.

1:12:08.338 --> 1:12:11.073
Run away!

1:12:44.707 --> 1:12:46.476
Michael?

1:12:49.712 --> 1:12:51.314
Michael?

1:13:15.538 --> 1:13:18.106
Michael?

1:13:20.209 --> 1:13:21.878
Hello?

1:13:37.627 --> 1:13:39.829
I heard a scream.

1:13:39.862 --> 1:13:43.131
I'm okay.
I just...

1:13:43.165 --> 1:13:44.734
It's nothing.

1:13:47.169 --> 1:13:49.872
I don't know if you remember me.

1:13:49.906 --> 1:13:51.841
I'm Charlie's granddaughter.

1:13:54.277 --> 1:13:56.846
I was little
the last time I saw you.

1:14:00.850 --> 1:14:03.252
We've been calling.

1:14:03.286 --> 1:14:05.254
No one answered.

1:14:05.288 --> 1:14:07.490
We unplugged the phone.

1:14:07.523 --> 1:14:10.193
My mom...

1:14:10.226 --> 1:14:12.829
I guess she wanted someone here
to know.

1:14:15.632 --> 1:14:17.667
My grandpa died.

1:14:18.968 --> 1:14:20.403
He, um...

1:14:22.772 --> 1:14:26.542
He shot himself two nights ago.

1:14:26.576 --> 1:14:29.312
Wait, I don't understand.

1:14:29.345 --> 1:14:31.381
I don't...

1:14:31.414 --> 1:14:34.450
Charlie died?

1:14:34.484 --> 1:14:37.620
We thought you should know.

1:14:39.589 --> 1:14:40.890
I said I'd come out here.

1:14:40.923 --> 1:14:42.191
I just...

1:14:44.293 --> 1:14:46.663
I thought I'd come and see.

1:14:46.696 --> 1:14:49.232
He was here. No.

1:14:49.265 --> 1:14:51.634
I just saw him.
That's not possible.

1:14:51.668 --> 1:14:53.403
They found him.

1:15:00.843 --> 1:15:03.279
I'm sorry about your mama.

1:15:08.785 --> 1:15:10.486
You should...

1:15:10.520 --> 1:15:12.689
You should come inside.

1:15:12.722 --> 1:15:15.191
Do you need help, Louise?

1:15:17.493 --> 1:15:19.462
I have to check on Dad.

1:15:28.471 --> 1:15:29.806
Come on in.
I just want to check him.

1:15:29.839 --> 1:15:31.808
I-I-I'm glad someone's here.

1:15:31.841 --> 1:15:34.444
To be honest,
th-th-this morning...

1:15:34.477 --> 1:15:37.246
Well, it's just...

1:15:37.280 --> 1:15:38.848
do you...

1:15:41.350 --> 1:15:43.386
Do you smell him?

1:15:47.724 --> 1:15:51.294
I bet you do.

1:15:52.361 --> 1:15:55.598
I smell him, too.

1:15:55.631 --> 1:15:58.601
He's close now.

1:16:01.604 --> 1:16:04.674
He's rotting.

1:16:12.381 --> 1:16:14.050
Get away from him!

1:16:14.083 --> 1:16:17.353
Get out!

1:16:24.660 --> 1:16:26.529
He's rotting.

1:16:26.562 --> 1:16:28.431
Get away from him.

1:16:28.464 --> 1:16:30.733
All alone.

1:16:30.767 --> 1:16:33.469
All alone.

1:16:33.503 --> 1:16:35.671
♪ All alone ♪

1:16:35.705 --> 1:16:37.039
Go!

1:16:37.073 --> 1:16:39.342
♪ All alone ♪

1:16:39.375 --> 1:16:40.810
Little girl.

1:17:30.493 --> 1:17:32.728
<i>Hello, you've reached
Michael Straker.</i>

1:17:32.762 --> 1:17:34.730
<i>Please leave a message,
and I'll call you back.</i>

1:17:34.764 --> 1:17:36.766
- <i>Thanks.</i>
- Damn it! Where are you?

1:17:36.799 --> 1:17:39.869
We have to get dad outta here.

1:17:42.839 --> 1:17:44.874
I'm sorry I'm late.

1:17:44.907 --> 1:17:47.977
I told Michael yesterday.
I hope that's okay.

1:17:48.010 --> 1:17:49.779
How's your dad doing?

1:17:53.449 --> 1:17:55.651
Fuck, fuck. Fuck.

1:18:38.661 --> 1:18:41.731
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

1:18:41.764 --> 1:18:42.932
Where are you?

1:18:42.965 --> 1:18:45.568
I woke up, and you were gone?

1:18:45.601 --> 1:18:46.936
I think something
happened to Charlie.

1:18:46.969 --> 1:18:48.838
I don't...
Where are you?

1:18:48.871 --> 1:18:51.440
<i>I'm driving.
Drove all night.</i>

1:18:51.474 --> 1:18:54.777
I wasn't gonna
stay there anymore.

1:18:54.810 --> 1:18:58.047
No, no, no, no, wait.
You didn't really leave.

1:18:58.080 --> 1:19:00.650
Tell me you didn't,
tell me you didn't.

1:19:00.683 --> 1:19:02.551
<i>They need me at home.</i>

1:19:02.585 --> 1:19:04.453
Why didn't
you fucking come talk to me?!

1:19:04.487 --> 1:19:06.455
I can't believe you did this!

1:19:06.489 --> 1:19:07.657
<i>I knew you'd stay.</i>

1:19:13.562 --> 1:19:15.998
Damn it!

1:19:17.967 --> 1:19:20.002
You left me.

1:19:23.639 --> 1:19:27.210
You left me.

1:19:40.990 --> 1:19:44.194
You need to go, Louise.

1:19:44.227 --> 1:19:45.928
You're my brother.

1:19:45.962 --> 1:19:48.097
You're all I have left.

1:19:48.130 --> 1:19:49.699
I love Becky.

1:19:49.732 --> 1:19:51.734
I love my girls.

1:19:51.767 --> 1:19:55.171
But I'm still here.

1:19:55.205 --> 1:19:57.707
<i>They're my life.</i>

1:20:10.320 --> 1:20:12.189
What about dad, huh?

1:20:12.222 --> 1:20:14.623
You even give a shit about him?

1:20:14.657 --> 1:20:15.891
<i>He's gone.</i>

1:20:15.925 --> 1:20:17.026
<i>He's gone.</i>

1:20:17.059 --> 1:20:19.161
- Listen to me.
- No, he's not!

1:20:19.196 --> 1:20:21.298
Listen!

1:20:21.331 --> 1:20:24.000
We can't change this.
We don't matter.

1:20:24.033 --> 1:20:25.235
Yes, we do!

1:20:25.268 --> 1:20:27.204
<i>It won't wait much longer.</i>

1:20:27.237 --> 1:20:30.573
Save yourself.

1:20:30.606 --> 1:20:32.975
Michael?

1:21:22.158 --> 1:21:23.793
Why don't you hear him?!

1:21:23.826 --> 1:21:25.628
Listen!

1:21:25.661 --> 1:21:27.063
No!

1:21:27.096 --> 1:21:29.899
No! Leave!

1:21:37.940 --> 1:21:39.309
Jesus...

1:21:44.013 --> 1:21:46.383
...you're with me.

1:21:52.655 --> 1:21:54.391
I... I hear you.

1:21:54.424 --> 1:21:57.394
You're... You're with me.

1:21:57.427 --> 1:21:58.794
Jesus...

1:22:01.931 --> 1:22:05.335
Jesus...

1:22:05.368 --> 1:22:09.038
Jesus, I feel you.

1:22:39.869 --> 1:22:40.970
<i>Jesus loves you.</i>

1:22:41.003 --> 1:22:42.872
<i>Always there for you.</i>

1:23:11.800 --> 1:23:14.170
Becky!

1:23:21.511 --> 1:23:23.913
Y'all here?

1:23:29.785 --> 1:23:31.288
Hey?

1:23:34.790 --> 1:23:36.359
Becky?

1:24:24.541 --> 1:24:26.243
Baby?

1:24:34.116 --> 1:24:37.886
Girls?

1:24:37.920 --> 1:24:39.788
Girls?

1:24:47.963 --> 1:24:50.333
Oh, my God.

1:24:50.367 --> 1:24:53.869
My God.

1:27:10.473 --> 1:27:12.475
I have to go.

1:27:17.079 --> 1:27:20.550
I'm sorry.

1:28:15.103 --> 1:28:17.207
I can't.

1:28:17.240 --> 1:28:19.442
I can't. I can't.

1:28:19.476 --> 1:28:21.678
I can't.

1:28:46.336 --> 1:28:48.705
I'm here.

1:28:48.738 --> 1:28:51.374
I'm here.

1:28:51.407 --> 1:28:52.742
I won't leave you.

1:28:52.775 --> 1:28:55.077
Louise!

1:28:58.681 --> 1:29:01.751
Michael?!

1:29:01.784 --> 1:29:03.353
Are you there?

1:29:07.423 --> 1:29:11.194
Louise! Help me!

1:29:11.227 --> 1:29:14.297
Help me!

1:29:14.330 --> 1:29:15.498
Help me, please! Help me!

1:29:15.532 --> 1:29:17.233
Help me! Louise, help me!

1:29:19.101 --> 1:29:21.704
Get away!

1:29:41.524 --> 1:29:43.226
I love you.

1:29:47.397 --> 1:29:51.301
I won't leave you.

1:30:17.159 --> 1:30:18.828
Daddy...

1:30:24.934 --> 1:30:28.271
Don't leave me.

1:30:31.474 --> 1:30:33.843
Don't leave me.

1:30:47.323 --> 1:30:49.492
Daddy...

1:30:49.525 --> 1:30:51.159
Daddy!

1:30:51.194 --> 1:30:52.795
Daddy!

1:30:52.829 --> 1:30:58.935
♪ Every trials and temptations ♪

1:30:58.968 --> 1:31:00.937
Mama?

1:31:00.970 --> 1:31:06.174
♪ Is there trouble anywhere? ♪

1:31:06.209 --> 1:31:09.612
♪ What a friend we have ♪

1:31:09.646 --> 1:31:11.179
♪ In Jesus ♪
